Ƙarfin Tide a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Wani rahoto da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa Red Tide tana da ƙarfi sosai a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton yanayin yanayin ƙasa a yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier, wanda ke nuna cewa yanayin yana raguwa.
Red Tide mai ban sha'awa ya kai tsibirai masu ɗakuna 130 daga kudancin Pinellas zuwa arewacin lardin Lee.
Za a iya samun wuraren zama a cikin gidaje 10 daga bishiyoyi zuwa tsibirin a yankin Hillsborough, amma a wasu wurare a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga Red Tide a gundumar Pasco.
An bayar da rahoton cewa a makon da ya gabata, an samu karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Pinellas zuwa yankin tsibirin, karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Hillsborough zuwa yankin tsibirin, wanda ya kai ga karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Manatee, wanda ya kai ga karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Sarasota zuwa yankin tsibirin, wanda ya kai ga karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Charlotte, wanda ya kai ga karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Lee zuwa yankin tsibirin, da kuma karuwar wutar lantarki daga yankin Collier.
An ci gaba da zargin da ake yi mini na ciwon kirji a yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier.
